{"name":"Amulet of the Black Skull: Black Skull Transformation","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Amulet of the Black Skull","keys":["d100","Transformation"],"diceKeys":["d100"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The symbol of Acererak is burned into your flesh, a curse that can only be removed with a remove curse spell or similar magic. Until the curse ends, your hit points can’t be restored by magic.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,20],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"YaDdkhVdnaxyKHXT"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"You grow larger as if affected by an enlarge/reduce spell, except the effect lasts for 1 hour.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[21,35],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"Iq80h8b3UFR0jega"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"You grow smaller as if affected by an enlarge/reduce spell, except the effect lasts for 1 hour.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[36,50],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"WszsPDEVnyGqJIJh"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"You arrive at the destination wearing nothing but the amulet of the black skull. Everything else that you were wearing or carrying appears in a random unoccupied space within 100 feet of you.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[51,70],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"cs6a89oyzRlExo5X"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"You are paralyzed for 1 minute or until this effect is ended with a lesser restoration spell or similar magic.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[71,95],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"rjYDnNUyMLQuaUxI"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"You become petrified. This effect can be ended only with a greater restoration spell or similar magic.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[96,100],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"UcEfFKG1yp0mnvfE"}],"formula":"d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"ownership":{"default":0,"7zB0QH211uvK7gvA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1677680227515,"modifiedTime":1677680227515,"lastModifiedBy":"7zB0QH211uvK7gvA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"3TPXbMfOc9l2TEHS"}
