"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Halfling, lightfoot","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[61,68],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"VLMJK91LoRYx94Bo"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Halfling, stout","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[69,76],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"i8ir5jFlowuBY48U"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Human","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[77,96],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"UuxRWjEsNwwmuZVN"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Tiefling","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[97,100],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"dpDMTuIAJNohMuFS"}],"formula":"d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"ownership":{"default":0,"7zB0QH211uvK7gvA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1677679530737,"modifiedTime":1677679530737,"lastModifiedBy":"7zB0QH211uvK7gvA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"3fXuZAJDtf0Ep1Kh"}
{"name":"Sling Bullets of Althemone: Magic Sling Bullets","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Sling Bullets of Althemone","keys":["d4","Bullet"],"diceKeys":["d4"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<strong>Banishment. </strong> A creature that takes damage from this bullet must succeed on a DC 15 Charisma saving throw or be banished as though affected by the banishment spell.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,1],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"cRvhtMzWhLVIaXkc"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<strong>Fulguration.</strong> On a hit, this bullet deals an extra [[/r 2d8[lightning] # Lightning damage]]  damage to its target. All other creatures within 10 feet of the target must each succeed on a DC 15 Constitution saving throw or take [[/r 1d8[thunder] # Thunder damage]]  damage.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[2,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"4bp1bFmxQAk77DkQ"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<strong>Stunning.</strong> On a hit, this bullet deals an extra [[/r 1d10[force] # Force damage]]  damage, and the target is stunned until the end of your next turn.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,3],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"Lx6Fi70mAWthOjKB"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<strong>Tracking.</strong> A creature that takes damage from this bullet is marked with a glowing rune where the bullet hit. The mark lasts 24 hours. While the creature is marked, you always know the direction to it.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[4,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"zXEk7Zy5ByD3qg6f"}],"formula":"d4","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"ownership":{"default":0,"7zB0QH211uvK7gvA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1677680311557,"modifiedTime":1677680311557,"lastModifiedBy":"7zB0QH211uvK7gvA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"5SEA8pDXdG2PdPu5"}
{"name":"Summon Lesser Demons: Demons Summoned","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Summon Lesser Demons","keys":["d6","Demons Summoned"],"diceKeys":["d6"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Two demons of challenge rating 1 or lower","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,2],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"CKfhYscpwiSXHXJF"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Four demons of challenge rating 1/2 or lower","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[3,4],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"RcjN5sW1DdPcuLSt"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Eight demons of challenge rating 1/4 or lower","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[5,6],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"ixKqmQuI6MAdw25q"}],"formula":"d6","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"ownership":{"default":0,"7zB0QH211uvK7gvA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1677679530819,"modifiedTime":1677679530819,"lastModifiedBy":"7zB0QH211uvK7gvA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"7dglaUFL0l4Q3lIw"}
{"name":"Sphere of Annihilation: Result","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Sphere of Annihilation","keys":["d100","Result"],"diceKeys":["d100"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The sphere is destroyed.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,50],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"Wdqtv3cejvvAErni"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"The sphere moves through the portal or into the extradimensional space.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[51,85],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"6F4CnW0nvhA5B6JN"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"A spatial rift sends each creature and object within 180 feet of the sphere, including the sphere, to a random plane of existence.","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[86,100],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"x7iZ4hN1BrI5HVUk"}],"formula":"d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"ownership":{"default":0,"7zB0QH211uvK7gvA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1677679771190,"modifiedTime":1677679771190,"lastModifiedBy":"7zB0QH211uvK7gvA"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"ARgjKnWsOPq4TRNU"}
{"name":"Horn of Valhalla: Four types of horn of Valhalla are known to exist, each made of a different metal. The horn's type determines how many berserkers answer its summons, as well as the requirement for its use. The GM chooses the horn's type or determines it randomly.","flags":{"ddbimporter":{"parentName":"Horn of Valhalla","keys":["d100","Horn Type","Berserkers Summoned","Requirement"],"diceKeys":["d100"]}},"img":"icons/svg/d20-grey.svg","description":"","results":[{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>[[+ 100]] ([[/r + 100]])</b>01-40\n\n<b>Horn Type</b>Silver\n\n<b>Berserkers Summoned</b>[[/r 2d4]]2\n\n<b>Requirement</b>None","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[1,40],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"zegG3x8wyBjjcjLy"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>[[+ 100]] ([[/r + 100]])</b>41-75\n\n<b>Horn Type</b>Brass\n\n<b>Berserkers Summoned</b>[[/r 3d4]]3\n\n<b>Requirement</b>Proficiency with all simple weapons","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[41,75],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"qKUKBl57KXktJxq3"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>[[+ 100]] ([[/r + 100]])</b>76-90\n\n<b>Horn Type</b>Bronze\n\n<b>Berserkers Summoned</b>[[/r 4d4]]4\n\n<b>Requirement</b>Proficiency with all medium armor","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[76,90],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"7Qj6HBIbNLBSCtEd"},{"flags":{},"type":0,"text":"<b>[[+ 100]] ([[/r + 100]])</b>91-100\n\n<b>Horn Type</b>Iron\n\n<b>Berserkers Summoned</b>[[/r 5d4]]5\n\n<b>Requirement</b>Proficiency with all martial weapons","img":"icons/svg/d20-black.svg","weight":1,"range":[91,100],"drawn":false,"documentCollection":"","documentId":null,"_id":"lP0xLvA6qLcNIrzN"}],"formula":"d100","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"ownership":{"default":0,"7zB0QH211uvK7gvA":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.1.5","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1677679873685,"modifiedTime":1677679